source.title: Ancient Sumerian Texts Reveal Terrifying Knowledge About Human Races | History for Sleep
source.description:
What if the oldest civilization on Earth never forgot where we came from—only hid it?
In the silent deserts of Mesopotamia, archaeologists uncovered clay tablets older than any holy book. Written in the language of the gods, these ancient Sumerian texts tell a story of human creation that predates religion, challenges evolution, and whispers of beings who shaped mankind in their own image.

This long-form documentary explores fifteen layers of mystery buried within those tablets—
from the Anunnaki creation myths and the flood before Genesis,
to the genetic experiments described as “clay mixed with divine blood,”
and the hidden archives sealed beneath temples for millennia.

Was humanity engineered?
Why did the gods leave—and what remains of them in our DNA?
Each part of this story unfolds like a dream you half-remember, told in a voice meant to calm you, yet leave you awake at the edge of revelation.

So before you fall asleep tonight, listen closely.
#AncientSumeria #ForbiddenHistory #Anunnaki #LostCivilizations #HumanOrigins
